channel.title: Question!
channel.description:
Will there be more chance that Jagex will catch me if i use an 508 source with working G.E. and real skill interfaces instead of a normal 508 source without G.E. etc.?

item.title: Question!
item.dc:creator: @Da_Vinci Da Vinci
item.description:
@Da_Vinci wrote:

[quote=“someone2, post:3, topic:353061”][quote author=Dealt link=topic=449374.msg3296831#msg3296831 date=1281007026]
they probably wont target a little server with little to no players on it
[/quote]
Oh, so the only thing that counts for them is players? So, big servers with much people like Frugooscape?[/quote]

Frugoo was something new and was very big, but regular servers with like 30-60 people on will not get targeted, you should start taking precautions when you hit 200+. Aka warning messages on your site, etc.

~Leo.
